nodes.text: Yu Dakar was a female Twi'lek who worked as a vendor on the Keylander Station during the the events of the Conquest of Makeb. She would be later found on the moon CZ-198 during the Seizure of CZ-198.
She was later removed in Game Update 5.0 on November 29, 2016, which retired the PvP and PvE gear vendors in favor of the Command system.
